  "title": "connectRefinementList: returns one 'currentRefinement' instead of all.",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\n\r\nbug\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\n`currentRefinement` is only the one of the refinements\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nIt should give an array of all of the current refinements.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What browsers are impacted? Which versions?**\r\n\r\nall\r\n\r\n**Bug: possible solution**\r\n\r\nuse `filter` instead of `find`, find only returns one element, filter returns an array.\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n\r\ninstantsearch.js \"v2\"\r\n",
